ime may become still more violent”}-, The Economist, dated 11 Feb 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Brian Stewart |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/is-iran-s-new-charm-offensive-real-1.1865464 |title=Is Iran's new 'charm offensive' real? |publisher=cbc.ca |date= |accessdate=2014-03-12 |archive-date=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140205020006/http://www.cbc.ca/news/is-iran-s-new-charm-offensive-real-1.1865464 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年8月25日，时任总统[[马哈茂德·艾哈迈迪内贾德|马哈茂德·艾哈迈迪内贾德]]在一次黎巴嫩电视台新闻采访中表示，暴力行动应当停止，“叙利亚政府和人民“应当进行对话。”艾哈迈迪内贾德说：“当人民和他们的领导间存在问题时，他们应坐下来解决问题，形成共识，远离暴力。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/08/201182582619939913.html|agency=Al Jazeera English|date=25 August 2011|accessdate=25 August 2011|title=Syrian tanks 'resume shelling' eastern town|archive-date=2011-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006075353/http://english.aljazeera.net//news/middleeast/2011/08/201182582619939913.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，8月26日，他告诉卡塔尔的埃米尔哈马德·本·哈利法·阿勒萨尼，他认为任何“外国霸权势力介入国家内政将会导致局势复杂化。”<ref>{{cite news|agency=Dawn|date=26 August 2011|url=http://www.dawn.com/2011/08/26/region-must-solve-issues-on-its-own-iran-tells-qatar.html|accessdate=26 August 2011|title=Region must solve issues on its own: Iran tells Qatar|archive-date=2011-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111231102816/http://www.dawn.com/2011/08/26/region-must-solve-issues-on-its-own-iran-tells-qatar.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

